Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:38.48,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,so I'll have to knock his socks off with \Nmagnificent magic while I steal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.74,Main Dialog,,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:
